text: Welschenrohr () was a municipality in Thal in the canton of Solothurn in Switzerland. On 1 January 2021, the former municipalities of Gänsbrunnen and Welschenrohr merged to form the new municipality of Welschenrohr-Gänsbrunnen. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Former municipalities of Solothurn
